column2: SELECT p.objID, p.ra, p.dec, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, dbo.fIAUFromEq(p.ra,p.[dec]) as SDSSname, str(p.ra,#,#) as ra, str(p.[dec],#,#) as dec, str(p.isoA_r,#,#) as dmaj, str(p.isoB_r,#,#) as dmin, str(p.isoPhi_r,#,#) as PA, p.type,  str(p.u,#,#) as mu, str(p.Err_u,#,#) as emu, str(p.g,#,#) as mg, str(p.Err_g,#,#) as emg, str(p.r,#,#) as mr, str(p.Err_r,#,#) as emr,  str(p.i,#,#) as mi, str(p.Err_i,#,#) as emi, str(p.z,#,#) as mz, str(p.Err_z,#,#) as emz, str(p.extinction_u,#,#) as Ag_u,  str(p.extinction_g,#,#) as Ag_g, str(p.extinction_r,#,#) as Ag_r,  str(p.extinction_i,#,#) as Ag_i, str(p.extinction_z,#,#) as Ag_z, p.specObjID FROM #x x, #upload u, BESTDR6..PhotoObj as p  WHERE u.up_id = x.up_id and x.objID=p.objID ORDER BY x.up_id
